street_name: Land Bound By Chancellor's Road, Distillery Road And Winslow Road, Including Sections Of Thames Path
description: Submission of reserved matters relating to external appearance and landscaping for Building B, pursuant to hybrid planning permission ref: 2011/00407/COMB granted 23rd December 2011, comprising a mixed use development of 167 new homes (938sqm GIA) of ground floor commercial floorspace (use classes A1-A4, D1/D2),  landscaped open space and parking provision.
